    <description>PE - When the stage of a Billing Upsell or Experience Curriculum opportunity is updated, this flow checks if it&apos;s the latest Billing Upsell opportunity. If so, it updates the corresponding field on the associated Account with this stage value. (Revenue.io Implementation Project)
12/21/23 - PE - Added contact records to be stamped with the opportunity stage as well.
01/03/24 - PE - Adjusted the flow to compare the creation date of each opportunity based on their record type.
01/04/24 - PE - Adjusted flow so if a contact is added to the opportunity, then the stage is stamped on that contact.
02/23/24 - PE Updated node that identifies contact on a new opportunity.
04/25/24 - PE - Updated flow to wipe out values from the previous contact when linked contact gets updated.</description>
    <environments>Default</environments>
    <formulas>
        <name>forB_IsNew</name>
        <dataType>Boolean</dataType>
        <expression>{!$Record__Prior.Id} = null</expression>
    </formulas>
    <formulas>
        <name>forT_OpportunityStage</name>
        <dataType>String</dataType>
        <expression>TEXT({!$Record.StageName})</expression>
    </formulas>
